column5: I'm looking for the list of Master Anglers for Northwest Ontario for the year 2001 ! Any help ????
Try looking up the Ontario government website, they would be the ones who publish it, so they might be able to send you a copy. Or let you know how you can get one.I'll take a look.
If you find anything please let me know !!Thanks Eric !
Manitoba has a Master Angler program but I have never heard of one in Ontario.
